}}

The '''Lucky Incense''' is a type of battle item. It temporarily boosts the player's money gained by 50% for 30 seconds.


==Details==
===Description===
+50% Bonus to money gained

===Acquisition===
{{ItemPrice/head‎|Battle items}}
{{ItemPrice|Dungeon Drop|Random}}
{{ItemPrice|Lavander Town|{{pdollar}}2,000}}
{{ItemPrice|Lilycove City|{{pdollar}}2,000}}
{{ItemPrice|Veilstone City|{{pdollar}}2,000}}
{{ItemPrice|Poké Mart|{{pdollar}}2,000}}
|}
|}

== Trivia ==
* This Lucky Incense shares its name, design and function with the official Lucky Incense from the Pokémon franchise. 


